 PhonepayPlus, the Office of Fair Trading, the Info</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">rmation Commissioner’s Office, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the DCMS, Home Office and Department for Education on child safety issues.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">  Our commitment </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">to policy engagement, therefore, has been and remains very strong</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">, but there are many issues and bodies to deal with</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="11" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Telef</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ó</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">nica also</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> offers the foll</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">owing o</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">bservation</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> on the key issues and challenge</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s in the field of online safety:</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span styl